race.comment: TAPO (5) gave a strong sight when runner-up at Wangaratta last week and is unbeaten at this track and trip. Has the speed to offset the wide draw and is a leading player. VERBOSITY (4) resumes off a sharp jump-out win and gets help at the weights with the 4kg claimer engaged. A big danger fresh. SIBEL (11) was far from disgraced last time when collared late, after scoring stylishly first-up. Can bounce back and give another bold sight. DARCEANDERMILL (12) strips fitter after a plain return at Yarra Valley and is capable of sharp improvement second-up. WRITTEN ROYALTY (1) is a proven fresh performer and must be respected resuming.
